CIS compliant system authentication profile with Centrify support
=================================================================

Selecting this profile will configure CIS Level 2 - Server compliant
system authentication.

AVAILABLE OPTIONAL FEATURES
---------------------------

with-centrify::
    Enable Centrify authentication.

with-mkhomedir::
    Enable automatic creation of home directories for users on their
    first login.

with-pamaccess::
    Check access.conf during account authorization.

with-systemd::
    Enable using systemd for user/group lookups.

with-yescrypt::
    Enable using yescrypt for password hashing algorithm.
